{"id": "1435943084981747762", "channel_id": "1435943084981747762", "type": 0, "author_id": "460676178253053957", "author_name": "dog_0630", "author_bot": false, "content": "入坑一個多月了\n感覺也是該準備挑戰融災更高分\n目前主線推完困難看這禮拜推不推的完忘卻\n有點在角色上的不知道怎麼分配資源\n把身上能擠出來的石頭都ALLIN塔薇後 \n打算先抽到+10 剩下等周年開始禮包抽完 再補+12還是怎樣的\n看著融災這樣每次都不知道自己該如何組隊才能正確分配資源在每關上\n有沒有隊伍組成推薦 雖然每期都會改 但我想先大致上看以我所擁有的資源中隊伍該如何組出來\n讓我下期有個參照物可以參考\n另外 塔薇抽出來卻完全沒想法要怎麼玩 真的就是想說要有隻強大的+12就ALLIN了\n還有那個體力 只剩下花銀芯跟體力包可以拿到體力嗎 沒有像前期過章節給大量的體力包的活動或禮包的東西嗎?\n感覺現在以我有的角色 可能摸個360-370就很緊繃了", "timestamp": "2025-11-06T10:45:09.992000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1435943085828734987", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3030643, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1435943084981747762/1435943085828734987/image.png?ex=69ccf736&is=69cba5b6&hm=c2a383e094253ba973f7dbcc13f921c1bffc7b92e24e4eab5cc27fe8cce34642&"}, {"id": "1435943086516867122", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3017695, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1435943084981747762/1435943086516867122/image.png?ex=69ccf736&is=69cba5b6&hm=cbbc55ce35b60526859be7ac89c590fb84cf6c6b9f60e007b969f9e8e8d1bfe6&"}, {"id": "1435943087179305002", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3106479, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1435943084981747762/1435943087179305002/image.png?ex=69ccf736&is=69cba5b6&hm=69c38809824f22f64576bfa9113f363cdce557ed6a91e85c28a35a461b58fb2c&"}, {"id": "1435943087695331388", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3211500, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1435943084981747762/1435943087695331388/image.png?ex=69ccf736&is=69cba5b6&hm=5f4130ad705ab1a2de3c8eca01099f2a7a4587a1784af44558bd37999e3d44ef&"}, {"id": "1435943088249110661", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3095156, "url": "https://cdn.discord